import React from 'react';
import {Box, Flex, Heading, HStack, IconButton, Image, ListIcon, Text, VStack} from "@chakra-ui/react";
import {AddIcon} from "@chakra-ui/icons";
import {BsListCheck, BsPlay} from "react-icons/all";

const LibraryPage = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Flex w={'100%'} bg={'gray.100'} direction={'column'}>
                <Box p={5} minW={'100'} bg={'white'} maxW={600} position={'relative'}>
                    <HStack spacing={5}>
                        <Box boxSize="100px">
                            <Image
                                src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/1205/1205526.png"
                                alt="Q"/>
                        </Box>
                        <VStack align={'start'}>
                            <HStack>
                                <Text color={'gray.500'} fontSize={12}>Quiz</Text>
                                <Text bg={'teal.100'} px={2} color={'gray.500'} fontSize={12}>Draft</Text>
                            </HStack>
                            <Text fontWeight={'medium'} fontSize={18}>Quiz name</Text>
                            <HStack spacing={4}>
                                <HStack>
                                    <IconButton size={"xs"} icon={<BsListCheck/>}/>
                                    <Text fontSize={12}>Q</Text>
                                </HStack>
                                <HStack>
                                    <IconButton size={"xs"} icon={<BsPlay/>}/>
                                    <Text fontSize={12}>Played 0 times</Text>
                                </HStack>
                            </HStack>
                            <Text>{Date.now()}</Text>
                        </VStack>
                    </HStack>
                </Box>
            </Flex>
        </>
    );
};

export default LibraryPage;
